metadata.name: Colorful Thoughts
metadata.description:
The powerful mind and colorful thoughts of a woman drives the future she builds by speaking the nurturing words to spread her wisdom!

Expanding your Imagination! Exclusive Imagination AI Art for collectors that love the outside world!
Our first generation of collections will be to benefit specific social causes across the globe.
Our first collection 100% Of Proceeds will go to benefit charities & scholarships benefiting young women!
Each piece will also be accompanied by a 1/1 signed print on METAL!
